sentence: Yet Mr. Trump snubbed him at the rally and instead praised a rival candidate, Tudor Dixon, who had held her own Mar-a-Lago fund-raiser in February.
title: Mar-a-Lago Machine: Trump as a Modern-Day Party Boss
